<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>dk.pracedru.Symbolical</id>
  <name>Symbolical</name>
  <summary>A math document application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>This application will give you the opertunity to setup a calculation docu with
    perfectly formated math equations. You can include some text fields and images to
    the documentation. The math fields include the ability to make units, functions and
    evaluations.</p>
  </description>
